{{vgname|双人成行|en=It Takes Two}}是一款由{{Internal link helper/en|霧影工作室|Hazelight Studios}}开发，[[艺电|艺电]]以EA Originals为名发行的[[动作冒险游戏|动作冒险]][[平台游戏|平台游戏]]，于2021年3月26日在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]、[[PlayStation_5|PlayStation 5]]、[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]和[[Xbox_Series_X/S|Xbox Series X/S]]平台发行。和Hazelight的首款作品《[[逃出生天_(遊戲)|越獄搭檔]]》相同，本作不支持单人游玩，只能进行在线或本地双人分屏合作。

据开发商披露，{{截至|2021|10}}，该游戏已销售300万份<ref>{{Cite web|title=Three. Million. Units. Sold|url=https://twitter.com/hazelightgames/status/1448262718281109505|access-date=2021-12-16|author=Hazelight Studios|date=2021-10-13|work=推特|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220217034507/https://twitter.com/hazelightgames/status/1448262718281109505|archive-date=2022-02-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==游戏玩法==
《双人成行》是一款带有[[平台游戏|平台游戏]]元素的[[动作冒险游戏|动作冒险游戏]]，专为多人[[分割畫面|分屏]]合作游戏设计，这意味着必须通过本地或在线模式与另一个玩家共同游玩。游戏采用了来自各种[[电子游戏类型|电子游戏类型]]的大量[[游戏机制|游戏机制]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.polygon.com/2020/12/10/22167732/it-takes-two-game-friend-pass-release-date-trailer-details-gameplay|title=The new co-op game from the A Way Out team lets multiplayer pals play free|first=Ryan|last=Gilliam|work=[[Polygon|Polygon]]|date=2020-12-10|access-date=2021-01-20|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211014826/https://www.polygon.com/2020/12/10/22167732/it-takes-two-game-friend-pass-release-date-trailer-details-gameplay|dead-url=no}}</ref>，这些游戏机制与故事和关卡的主题有关。例如，在一个关卡中，科迪获得了时间倒流的能力，而小梅则可以复制自己。玩家必须相互配合，利用这些能力推进剧情。游戏中还有大量的[[小游戏|迷你游戏]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.videogamer.com/news/it-takes-two-offers-a-look-at-its-co-operative-gameplay-in-latest-trailer|title=It Takes Two offers a look at its co-operative gameplay in latest trailer|first=Ben|last=Borthwick|work=VideoGamer.com|date=2021-02-23|accessdate=2021-03-17|archive-date=2021-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223103609/https://www.videogamer.com/news/it-takes-two-offers-a-look-at-its-co-operative-gameplay-in-latest-trailer|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==剧情==
科迪（Cody）和小梅（May）是一对感情破裂即将走向离婚的夫妻。两人把离婚的想法告诉女儿罗丝（Rose），罗丝带着自己亲手做的父母样子的玩偶躲进家中小屋，试图通过“[[过家家|过家家]]”的方式让两人破镜重圆。小梅和科迪因女儿的泪水滴在娃娃身上而被困在娃娃的身体里。为了回到女儿身边，两人在爱之书哈金博士（Dr. Hakim）的指导下，展开一场彼此依赖的冒险。

==开发==
[[约瑟夫·法尔斯|约瑟夫·法尔斯]]担任游戏监制，他曾任Hazelight的《[[逃出生天_(遊戲)|越獄搭檔]]》（2018）和Starbreeze Studios的《[[兄弟：双子传说|兄弟：双子传说]]》（''Brothers: A Tale of Two Sons''）的监制。在2018年发布《越獄搭檔》后，团队决定再制作一款仅有合作模式的电子游戏，进一步改进和扩展《越獄搭檔》所引入的游戏概念<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/not-even-ea-thought-a-way-out-would-sell-josef-fares-on-why-hes-making-games-in-a-genre-he-had-to-invent|title='Not Even EA Thought A Way Out Would Sell' - Josef Fares on Why He's Making Games in a Genre He Had to Invent|first=Joe|last=Skrebels|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2020-01-15|access-date=2021-01-20|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115122103/https://www.ign.com/articles/not-even-ea-thought-a-way-out-would-sell-josef-fares-on-why-hes-making-games-in-a-genre-he-had-to-invent|dead-url=no}}</ref>。开发团队努力确保游戏玩法与叙事有联系，随着故事的展开，游戏机制也会有相应的变化。法尔斯推动他的团队尽可能多地加入一些机制和设定，因为他认为如果一个游戏机制被反复使用，它将变得“不那么特别”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/it-takes-two-could-take-15-hours-to-complete-and-should-win-a-world-record-for-mechanics-says-josef-fares|title=It Takes Two Could Take 15 Hours to Complete and Should Win a World Record for Mechanics, Says Josef Fares|first=Joe|last=Skrebels|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2020-12-15|access-date=2021-01-20|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211020254/https://www.ign.com/articles/it-takes-two-could-take-15-hours-to-complete-and-should-win-a-world-record-for-mechanics-says-josef-fares|dead-url=no}}</ref>。法尔斯将这款游戏描述为“[[浪漫喜剧|浪漫喜剧]]”，他为游戏中的关键角色之一哈金博士提供了[[动作捕捉|动作捕捉]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/it-takes-two-and-the-relentless-positivity-of-josef-fares/1100-6485340/|title=It Takes Two And The Relentless Positivity Of Josef Fares|first=Steve|last=Watts|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|date=2020-12-10|access-date=2021-01-20|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211015233/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/it-takes-two-and-the-relentless-positivity-of-josef-fares/1100-6485340/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

和《越獄搭檔》相同，《双人成行》在[[艺电|艺电]]的EA Originals计划下发行。该计划让Hazelight保留了完全的创意控制权，同时在收回开发成本后可获得游戏的大部分利润<ref>{{cite web|url=https://venturebeat.com/2017/06/11/a-way-out-creator-if-you-dont-like-it-you-can-break-my-legs/|title=A Way Out creator Josef Fares: 'If you don't like it, you can break my legs'|first=Josef|last=Fares|work=[[VentureBeat|VentureBeat]]|date=2017-06-11|access-date=2020-12-11|archive-date=2017-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170611212242/https://venturebeat.com/2017/06/11/a-way-out-creator-if-you-dont-like-it-you-can-break-my-legs/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。EA在2019年6月首次宣布与Hazelight签订发行协议<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2019-06-08-ea-sign-fresh-indie-publishing-deals-with-zoink-glowmade-and-hazelight|title=EA signs fresh indie publishing deals with Zoink, Glowmade and Hazelight|first=Christopher|last=Dring|work=Gameindustry.biz|date=2019-06-08|access-date=2021-01-20|archive-date=2019-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608220140/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2019-06-08-ea-sign-fresh-indie-publishing-deals-with-zoink-glowmade-and-hazelight|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏在2020年6月的EA Play期间正式亮相<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.polygon.com/2020/6/18/21296330/ea-play-2020-josef-fares-it-takes-two|title=New co-op game from A Way Out creator, It Takes Two, launches in 2021|first=Julia|last=Lee|work=[[Polygon|Polygon]]|date=2020-06-18|access-date=2021-01-20|archive-date=2020-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200619120803/https://www.polygon.com/2020/6/18/21296330/ea-play-2020-josef-fares-it-takes-two|dead-url=no}}</ref>。EA和Hazelight为游戏推出了好友通行证（Friend's Pass），允许购买游戏的玩家向自己的朋友发出邀请，然后朋友可以免费和玩家一起玩游戏<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2020-12-11-heres-our-first-look-at-it-takes-two-gameplay|title=Here's our first look at It Takes Two gameplay|first=Wesley|last=Yin-Poole|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date=2020-12-11|access-date=2021-01-20|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211015141/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2020-12-11-heres-our-first-look-at-it-takes-two-gameplay|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《双人成行》于2021年3月26日在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]、[[PlayStation_5|PlayStation 5]]、[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]和[[Xbox_Series_X/S|Xbox Series X/S]]平台发行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.destructoid.com/stories/it-takes-two-is-an-out-of-control-co-op-adventure-from-the-makers-of-a-way-out-613034.phtml|title=It Takes Two is an out-of-control co-op adventure from the makers of A Way Out|first=Jordan|last=Devore|work=[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]|date=2020-12-10|access-date=2020-01-20|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211020553/https://www.destructoid.com/stories/it-takes-two-is-an-out-of-control-co-op-adventure-from-the-makers-of-a-way-out-613034.phtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

